databaseQueries.query: SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN jenis_transaksis.id IN (1,2) THEN transaksis.jumlah ELSE 0 END) - (SUM(CASE WHEN jenis_transaksis.id IN (3,4) THEN transaksis.jumlah ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN jenis_transaksis.id = 5 THEN transaksis.jumlah ELSE 0 END)) AS saldo FROM `transaksis` inner join `jenis_transaksis` on `transaksis`.`jenis_transaksi_id` = `jenis_transaksis`.`id` WHERE `transaksis`.`user_id` = 2 and `transaksis`.`void` = 0

SELECT `kategori_transaksi_id`, `kategori_transaksis`.`nama`, SUM(jumlah) as total_jumlah FROM `transaksis` inner join `kategori_transaksis` on `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id` = `kategori_transaksis`.`id` WHERE `transaksis`.`user_id` = 2 and `void` = 0 and month(`transaksis`.`created_at`) = '12' and `transaksis`.`jenis_transaksi_id` in (3, 4) GROUP BY `kategori_transaksi_id`, `kategori_transaksis`.`nama` ORDER BY `total_jumlah` DESC LIMIT 7
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 2) and `void` = 0
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 2) and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (3, 4) and `void` = 0
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` = 5 and `void` = 0
SELECT * FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `void` = 0 and date(`tanggal`) >= '2023-12-03' and date(`tanggal`) <= '2023-12-10' LIMIT 7

SELECT `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, SUM(transaksis.jumlah) / anggarans.jumlah * 100 AS persentase FROM `transaksis` inner join `anggarans` on `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id` = `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id` WHERE `transaksis`.`user_id` = 2 and `transaksis`.`void` = 0 and `anggarans`.`user_id` = 2 and month(`transaksis`.`tanggal`) = '12' GROUP BY `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id`, `anggarans`.`jumlah`, `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id`
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 2) and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'
SELECT `nama`, `id`, (401034904 * value / 100) AS jumlah FROM `kategori_anggarans` WHERE `user_id` = 2
SELECT sum(`jumlah`) as aggregate FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `jenis_transaksi_id` in (1, 2) and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'

SELECT `kategori_anggarans`.`id` as `id_kategori_anggaran`, `kategori_anggarans`.`value`, SUM(transaksis.jumlah) as total_jumlah FROM `kategori_anggarans` left join `anggarans` on `kategori_anggarans`.`id` = `anggarans`.`kategori_anggaran_id` left join `transaksis` on `anggarans`.`kategori_transaksi_id` = `transaksis`.`kategori_transaksi_id` WHERE `anggarans`.`user_id` = 2 and `transaksis`.`user_id` = 2 and `transaksis`.`void` = 0 and month(`transaksis`.`tanggal`) = '12' GROUP BY `kategori_anggarans`.`id`, `kategori_anggarans`.`value`
SELECT * FROM `transaksis` WHERE `user_id` = 2 and `void` = 0 and month(`tanggal`) = '12'

SELECT `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` FROM `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` WHERE `model_has_roles`.`model_id` in (2) and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\\Models\\User'
